// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2021-1631 — Mass File Rename (blackmatter)
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: e35ce597-3bd7-58c1-bce5-09575aabe912

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
